HEADWORD: By-product
<hw>By"-prod`uct</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A secondary or
additional product; something produced, as in the course of a
manufacture, in addition to the principal product.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

